nodes.text: This Mon Calamari lived on the ocean-covered planet of Dac during the Battle of Mon Cala around 21 BBY and commanded a squadron of Mon Calamari soldiers that fought the Quarren and Separatist Aqua droids. He seemed relieved upon seeing captain Ackbar and went into battle alongside him. He was later seen captured by the enemy and while he was transported to a prison camp, he was met by Prince Lee-Char, who told him and the others not to loose hope.
